title: Week 10: Pivotal weekend for CFB playoff's rankings
description:
The crew discuss this weekend's huge matchups. The biggest matchups comes from the SEC with a battle between #1 Tennessee vs #3 Georgia, and #6 Alabama vs #10 LSU. Also, with the playoffs around the corner can we potentially see Ohio State or Michigan make it in with a loss? Another thing worth noting is who is the front runner for the Heisman award?
